  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK167">
<l>avvit taḻukkā ṟuṭaiyāṉaic ceyyava</l>
<l>ṭavvaiyaik kāṭṭi viṭum.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lakshmi envying (the prosperity) of the envious man will depart and introduce him to her sister.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
